snippet.title: PICROSS S GENESIS & Master System edition Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
A character editor has been added to the Nintendo Switch version of Picross S!
Select characters have been chosen to debut as Picross puzzles
from Sega's classic consoles, the Master System and Sega Genesis!
